WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.230
Good morning, family.

00:00:02.230 --> 00:00:02.240
I’m

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.909
going to talk to you about the time

00:00:03.909 --> 00:00:03.919
when

00:00:03.919 --> 00:00:05.670
Jesus woke me up in the middle

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:08.870
of the night and

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:13.190
ministered to me.

00:00:13.190 --> 00:00:13.200
This

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.029
was around October

00:00:16.039 --> 00:00:19.910
2014, and this experience forever

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:22.550
changed my life. I feel

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:24.310
in my heart that when I first started

00:00:24.310 --> 00:00:24.320
on

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:26.070
YouTube, I tried to tell you

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:28.390
all what he said, and I thought I

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:28.400
would

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:31.509
do it again because

00:00:31.519 --> 00:00:34.709
it gets buried by the algorithm.

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:36.229
Nobody

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:38.229
sees it, especially all the new faces

00:00:38.239 --> 00:00:41.590
here. I want to tell

00:00:41.590 --> 00:00:41.600
you

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.030
because this was an

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:44.310
experience I had with him that

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:47.470
changed my life forever.

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:52.069
I was sleeping

00:00:52.069 --> 00:00:52.079
when,

00:00:52.079 --> 00:00:53.910
all of a sudden, I felt a tap on my

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:55.670
right shoulder.

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:58.630
I was just laying in bed

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.270
on my side and I heard an

00:01:01.270 --> 00:01:01.280
audible voice say,

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:03.910
'Wake

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:07.270
up.'I

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.109
looked over, and

00:01:09.119 --> 00:01:12.469
Jesus was standing in my room.

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:13.910
Most people will ask, 'Was this a vision?'No, this was not a

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:16.789
vision. This

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:19.990
was real; he manifested in

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.830
my house. This was one of the only

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:24.149
times it

00:01:24.149 --> 00:01:24.159
was

00:01:24.159 --> 00:01:26.310
not an open vision.

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:28.469
This was a face-to-face

00:01:28.479 --> 00:01:30.630
experience with him touching

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.950
my shoulder and waking me up.

00:01:33.960 --> 00:01:37.190
It startled me so much

00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:37.200
because

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.030
when

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.550
you're waking up

00:01:42.550 --> 00:01:42.560
and

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:44.069
rubbing your eyes, you don't recognize

00:01:44.069 --> 00:01:44.079
things immediately. I looked

00:01:44.079 --> 00:01:46.469
over and saw Jesus

00:01:46.469 --> 00:01:46.479
standing

00:01:46.479 --> 00:01:48.230
there. I felt his glory and

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.230
presence and thought, 'Am I

00:01:50.230 --> 00:01:50.240
dying?'My

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:52.550
initial reaction was that

00:01:52.550 --> 00:01:52.560
I was

00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:54.630
going home and he was coming to

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:57.749
get me. But he said, 'I've come to

00:01:57.759 --> 00:01:59.830
answer your prayers.'I

00:01:59.830 --> 00:01:59.840
asked,

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:02.069
'Lord,

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:03.910
what's

00:02:03.910 --> 00:02:03.920
happening?'All

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:07.109
of a sudden, I looked at my floor, and

00:02:07.109 --> 00:02:07.119
it

00:02:07.119 --> 00:02:09.150
was

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:12.309
alive. The glory of the Lord was so

00:02:12.319 --> 00:02:15.790
strong in my house that the floor was

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:18.150
breathing. A

00:02:18.160 --> 00:02:22.070
portal opened in my floor. I flipped my feet over the

00:02:22.070 --> 00:02:22.080
side

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.070
of my bed

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:26.309
and

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:28.150
sat

00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:30.710
there looking at

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:34.150
that portal below my feet. Jesus

00:02:34.150 --> 00:02:34.160
was

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:36.470
standing right there at my right hand.

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:38.229
I

00:02:38.239 --> 00:02:40.390
was

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:43.030
looking at this portal, and it

00:02:43.030 --> 00:02:43.040
was

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:45.830
alive; I could feel the air breathing.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:49.030
It was blowing my hair.

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:58.630
I could

00:02:58.640 --> 00:03:02.070
feel the breeze from the portal.

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:03.910
It was moving

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:06.710
like a whirlpool, with light

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.790
moving down and up

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:11.750
like a

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:13.910
waterfall.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:15.509
My wife was sleeping next to

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:17.110
me and never knew any of this happened;

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.990
she was out

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:22.229
cold.

00:03:22.239 --> 00:03:23.589
I said, 'Lord, what do you

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:25.390
want me to do?'He said,

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:27.910
'I want you to jump inside that

00:03:27.910 --> 00:03:27.920
portal.'I

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:30.869
said, 'You

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:32.229
want me to jump?'He said, 'Brandon,

00:03:32.239 --> 00:03:34.949
trust

00:03:34.949 --> 00:03:34.959
me.'I

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:36.949
looked at him because

00:03:36.949 --> 00:03:36.959
this was

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:38.470
all happening so fast

00:03:38.470 --> 00:03:38.480
and

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:40.789
it

00:03:40.789 --> 00:03:40.799
was

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:43.509
shocking.

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:50.149
Jesus was standing there

00:03:50.149 --> 00:03:50.159
in

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:52.550
a beautiful white robe,

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:54.710
and his hair was flowing

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:57.190
because the air from the portal was moving

00:03:57.190 --> 00:03:57.200
it.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:04:00.949
I

00:04:00.959 --> 00:04:03.110
said, 'Okay, Lord.'All of a sudden,

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:05.429
I pushed myself off

00:04:05.439 --> 00:04:07.830
the edge of the bed and went straight

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:11.350
down into that tunnel. It

00:04:11.350 --> 00:04:11.360
was

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:12.789
like Mario

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.149
Brothers on the Nintendo when you

00:04:14.149 --> 00:04:14.159
go

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:16.069
into the tunnel

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:17.909
and they transported you to

00:04:17.919 --> 00:04:19.909
another part. That's what it felt like.

00:04:21.919 --> 00:04:23.670
When I jumped inside of that

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:27.909
hole, I was taken to the past.

00:04:27.919 --> 00:04:29.830
I was standing at a

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:33.030
hospital where my wife and I had

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:36.030
our daughter, Megan. He said,

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:38.230
'Brandon, I'm giving you a

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:39.990
chance. You've asked me and asked me

00:04:41.960 --> 00:04:45.030
to go back in time. You always ask, "Lord, if I could

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:47.830
just go back in time

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:49.990
to

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.590
when she

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:54.790
got her

00:04:54.790 --> 00:04:54.800
shot

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:57.030
and stop that, I could keep her

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:58.749
from getting this severe

00:04:58.749 --> 00:04:58.759
autism."'I’ve

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:01.030
always said

00:05:01.030 --> 00:05:01.040
that

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.790
I would clean the bathrooms of

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.150
the church or vacuum the halls if I could just go back

00:05:04.150 --> 00:05:04.160
in time

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:05.749
and warn

00:05:05.749 --> 00:05:05.759
myself.

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:08.629
If I

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:17.029
could just give myself the

00:05:17.039 --> 00:05:18.710
opportunity to tell

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:23.110
myself not to do that, because

00:05:23.110 --> 00:05:23.120
it

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.390
wrecked my

00:05:24.390 --> 00:05:24.400
life

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:25.670
the way

00:05:25.670 --> 00:05:25.680
it

00:05:25.680 --> 00:05:28.350
has. I

00:05:28.350 --> 00:05:28.360
wished

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:30.950
I could have a redo.

00:05:33.880 --> 00:05:36.150
He said,

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:38.230
'I'm going to give you the time to go

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:41.670
and change the future. I want you to go

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:44.469
and tell yourself.'I ran up the

00:05:44.479 --> 00:05:46.870
stairs to the fourth floor of

00:05:46.870 --> 00:05:46.880
the

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:48.950
doctor's office.

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:55.350
I busted

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:58.390
through the doors and saw

00:05:58.390 --> 00:05:58.400
my

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:01.550
younger self sitting there with my

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:04.629
daughter and my wife. They were getting

00:06:04.639 --> 00:06:07.670
ready to administer the shot. I

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:11.950
said

00:06:11.950 --> 00:06:11.960
'Stop!'just

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:15.870
like that. I

00:06:15.880 --> 00:06:19.749
froze, and the younger me froze. I told

00:06:19.749 --> 00:06:19.759
the nurse to

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:22.150
stop and told

00:06:22.150 --> 00:06:22.160
my

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:25.510
younger

00:06:25.510 --> 00:06:25.520
self,

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:27.510
'Don't

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:29.909
do it.'All of a

00:06:29.919 --> 00:06:32.629
sudden, Jesus came and said, 'I want to

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:35.830
show you the power of a

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:37.909
choice.'He

00:06:37.919 --> 00:06:40.629
threw

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:42.629
his hand

00:06:42.639 --> 00:06:45.270
open and put a screen up in

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:48.230
front of my face. Everything froze in

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:52.390
time, and he showed me a future where Megan didn't get

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:56.150
that shot. He painted it all

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:58.870
out

00:07:01.479 --> 00:07:04.430
in front of me for each

00:07:04.440 --> 00:07:06.870
year. He said, 'Brandon, I want to

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:09.110
show you what happened by

00:07:09.110 --> 00:07:09.120
this

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:10.550
choice.'I

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.830
told him,

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:13.749
'Lord, you've called me to be

00:07:13.759 --> 00:07:15.830
a healing evangelist,

00:07:15.830 --> 00:07:15.840
but

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:18.150
I

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.749
can't pray for

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:21.430
people because I'll look like a

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:22.950
hypocrite while my own daughter is still

00:07:22.960 --> 00:07:24.710
overcome. I've laid hands on her

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:27.270
probably a thousand times and

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:30.629
never felt

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:32.230
the anointing

00:07:32.230 --> 00:07:32.240
go

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:34.790
into

00:07:36.230 --> 00:07:36.240
her.'I’ve

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:39.350
always kept this private.

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:41.189
I wouldn't even let

00:07:41.189 --> 00:07:41.199
anyone

00:07:41.199 --> 00:07:43.029
say

00:07:43.029 --> 00:07:43.039
the

00:07:43.039 --> 00:07:46.070
word

00:07:46.070 --> 00:07:46.080
'autistic.'I

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:48.390
would want

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:49.510
to fight you if

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:49.520
you did

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:51.510
because

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:52.950
faith calls those things that be not as

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:54.390
though they were.

00:07:54.390 --> 00:07:54.400
I

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.230
didn't

00:07:56.240 --> 00:07:57.670
even let the

00:07:57.680 --> 00:07:59.430
doctors diagnose her at

00:07:59.430 --> 00:07:59.440
first

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:01.430
because I was so upset;

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:03.029
I didn't want them speaking those

00:08:03.029 --> 00:08:03.039
words

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:04.230
because life and death

00:08:04.230 --> 00:08:04.240
are

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:05.749
in the power of the tongue. I got really flaky about it because I was scared of the diagnosis and didn't

00:08:05.759 --> 00:08:07.029
want

00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:11.350
anyone

00:08:17.230 --> 00:08:17.240
speaking

00:08:23.919 --> 00:08:25.830
anything over my child. I'm telling

00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:28.230
you all, it was bondage. And she

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:29.830
would rock in the corner and scream at

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:31.749
night all night long after it happened.

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:33.110
I'm telling you, it was

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:36.070
literal hell on earth for years before I

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:38.149
would allow them to diagnose her and for

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.149
her to get help through therapies

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:42.310
and stuff, because I was believing God by

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:43.589
faith because I'm the big

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:45.509
healing evangelist and because of all these

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:47.829
prophecies that were given over my life.

00:08:47.839 --> 00:08:50.630
So here I am.

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:53.190
The Lord threw all this out in front

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:55.750
of me and he said, "Brandon, I want to

00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:59.430
show you what happens with Megan."Now, Megan

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:02.790
is developing normally, but you're

00:09:02.800 --> 00:09:05.150
not

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:10.269
changing. The pressure from her

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:13.829
circumstance changes you. It puts you

00:09:13.839 --> 00:09:16.550
through the refiner's fire.

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.670
And he told me, "Brandon, I did

00:09:19.680 --> 00:09:24.030
not do this. I did not cause her to be

00:09:24.040 --> 00:09:27.350
autistic, but whatever the devil

00:09:27.350 --> 00:09:27.360
meant

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.750
for bad, I will turn it for good

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:33.190
in your favor. And no matter how bad the

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:35.350
circumstance is, I will always turn it

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:37.990
for good in your favor. Whatever the

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:40.870
devil meant for bad for

00:09:40.870 --> 00:09:40.880
you."But

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:43.030
he said, "I'm not the one that

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:45.829
caused the autism.

00:09:45.839 --> 00:09:47.750
It's a fallen world. Things happen. You

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:48.949
know what I'm

00:09:48.949 --> 00:09:48.959
saying?"That's

00:09:48.959 --> 00:09:50.070
the way

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.470
he painted the picture to me. I want

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.230
to say exactly what he said, but it's

00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:55.829
been so long that I'm forgetting some of

00:09:55.839 --> 00:09:57.430
the words, so you have to just bear

00:09:57.440 --> 00:09:59.350
with me here. I'm painting

00:09:59.360 --> 00:10:02.870
the picture of how Jesus told me.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:04.630
So he painted the picture in front

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:06.670
of me and I went from year to

00:10:06.680 --> 00:10:08.949
year. He said, "Brandon, do you see

00:10:08.959 --> 00:10:11.590
right here? You have a lot of

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:13.269
anger issues that you're still

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:14.790
overcoming."And

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:16.630
he said, "You were very verbally

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:19.030
abusive to your wife,"which

00:10:19.030 --> 00:10:19.040
I was.

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:21.110
I belittled her a lot when I first got

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:23.590
married. I was young and stupid

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.310
and I didn't handle myself like I

00:10:25.320 --> 00:10:28.230
should. And he said, because of this

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:31.910
right here, it

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:34.110
develops a wall between you and your

00:10:34.120 --> 00:10:37.509
wife over the course of time.

00:10:37.519 --> 00:10:41.750
Megan's developing normally, but he said

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:44.550
your wife leaves you right here—and he

00:10:44.560 --> 00:10:46.389
pointed out the year, which is nobody's

00:10:46.389 --> 00:10:46.399
business—but

00:10:46.399 --> 00:10:48.870
he told me, "She

00:10:48.870 --> 00:10:48.880
is

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:50.190
going to leave you right

00:10:50.200 --> 00:10:53.269
here and she takes your daughter and

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:54.670
they move to

00:10:54.670 --> 00:10:54.680
Texas."And

00:10:54.680 --> 00:10:57.509
he said, "And you see her

00:10:57.519 --> 00:11:00.790
every two weeks on the weekends. You

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:02.790
don't have full custody because she moves

00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:04.829
and lives with her

00:11:04.839 --> 00:11:08.230
mom. Whenever this takes place,

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:11.030
you see her on the

00:11:11.030 --> 00:11:11.040
weekends."And

00:11:11.040 --> 00:11:14.949
he said, Diana gets

00:11:14.959 --> 00:11:17.829
remarried to another man. And he showed

00:11:17.839 --> 00:11:20.710
me the man and said, "This is

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:22.470
when your wife gets remarried."And he

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:25.550
said, "Then you become very bitter and

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:28.310
angry because of the choices that

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:31.030
you've made. You're off track with your

00:11:31.040 --> 00:11:32.949
call and what I've called you

00:11:32.959 --> 00:11:36.430
to do because

00:11:36.440 --> 00:11:40.150
this is what's changing you. All

00:11:40.160 --> 00:11:42.470
this pressure from having a child with

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:45.350
special needs is molding your character.

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:47.870
It's breaking you down. It's making you

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:52.389
pliable in my hands. Yes, the

00:11:52.389 --> 00:11:52.399
pressure—I

00:11:52.399 --> 00:11:55.069
did not

00:11:55.079 --> 00:11:59.509
do it, but I will use it."Does that

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:01.150
make sense?

00:12:01.160 --> 00:12:05.190
So I saw the pressure of my daughter

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:08.069
every single year without having the

00:12:08.079 --> 00:12:09.910
pressure from this because she

00:12:09.920 --> 00:12:13.110
didn't have the autism anymore;

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:15.670
she became normal and she became an

00:12:15.670 --> 00:12:15.680
adult.

00:12:15.680 --> 00:12:18.629
And he said, "Brandon, your son was

00:12:18.639 --> 00:12:22.710
never born. Your son that your

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:25.790
wife has right now was never

00:12:25.800 --> 00:12:29.350
born, and your daughter that will be born

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:31.190
in the future

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:35.190
will not be born. And there is a call on

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:38.310
her life for the thousand years for

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:39.590
things that I'm going to do with a

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:42.150
thousand years. There are things that are

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:44.310
set in motion that will not be put in

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:47.670
motion because of choices."He said, "You

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:50.230
say that you've messed up your life and

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:52.870
you can't be used now because of

00:12:52.870 --> 00:12:52.880
Megan."But

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:55.389
he said,

00:12:55.399 --> 00:12:59.509
"Brandon, all things work together for

00:12:59.519 --> 00:13:02.310
good for those that love the Lord and

00:13:02.320 --> 00:13:04.069
are heirs and are called according to

00:13:04.079 --> 00:13:04.829
his

00:13:04.839 --> 00:13:07.670
purpose. You're not big enough to mess

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:08.829
up your

00:13:08.839 --> 00:13:13.269
life. You're not big enough to derail

00:13:13.279 --> 00:13:15.110
your

00:13:15.110 --> 00:13:15.120
life."He

00:13:15.120 --> 00:13:17.110
said, "If you are in right standing with

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:19.350
me and you keep yourself in right

00:13:19.360 --> 00:13:22.829
standing and seek me

00:13:22.839 --> 00:13:25.350
daily, building your relationship with

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:27.829
me, I will take what the devil

00:13:27.839 --> 00:13:29.590
meant for bad and turn it for good in

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:31.389
your

00:13:31.399 --> 00:13:34.710
favor. There's

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:37.509
not enough power in hell to derail

00:13:37.509 --> 00:13:37.519
the

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:40.470
call on your life, son. Even with how

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:42.310
bad you feel you've messed up with

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:44.870
this, I'll turn it around for good in

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:49.350
your favor if you keep seeking me."So I

00:13:49.360 --> 00:13:51.509
want to tell you this. Whenever he told

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:52.670
me

00:13:52.680 --> 00:13:56.710
this, I saw each year play out

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:58.790
before my face, up

00:13:58.800 --> 00:14:00.629
until that point. My son wasn't

00:14:00.639 --> 00:14:03.350
born; my youngest daughter

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:06.150
wasn't born. All these bad decisions

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:08.310
that I had made and the

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:10.629
pressure I had from having a child with

00:14:10.639 --> 00:14:14.269
special needs had molded me to what I am

00:14:14.279 --> 00:14:17.030
today. And God took what the devil meant

00:14:17.040 --> 00:14:18.870
for bad and he turned it around for good

00:14:18.880 --> 00:14:22.069
in my favor because it molded me and

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:24.230
created a better person out of

00:14:24.240 --> 00:14:26.949
me. If you've never been a caretaker of

00:14:26.959 --> 00:14:29.110
somebody with special needs whenever

00:14:29.120 --> 00:14:32.150
they're messing themselves or having

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:34.389
their cycle or going through the hell

00:14:34.399 --> 00:14:36.790
that I went through in the beginning,

00:14:36.800 --> 00:14:39.350
the tears that I cried... she only

00:14:39.360 --> 00:14:42.150
slept two hours a night. It was

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:44.110
awful. And that lasted for

00:14:44.120 --> 00:14:46.629
years. I would go to work and

00:14:46.639 --> 00:14:48.550
I would be so tired. I'd fall asleep

00:14:48.560 --> 00:14:49.990
laying against the wall and

00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:52.389
I'd catch myself because I was so tired

00:14:52.399 --> 00:14:54.790
cleaning toilets, and I was barely

00:14:54.800 --> 00:14:57.949
making any money at all,

00:14:57.959 --> 00:15:02.110
living on food stamps for

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:05.030
years. I'm doing this and my wife is

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:07.590
at home crying and I

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.870
can't wait to get home. I can't deal

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:12.509
with this anymore because Megan was so

00:15:12.519 --> 00:15:15.189
bad. And she'd say, "Can you come and

00:15:15.199 --> 00:15:17.269
relieve me and just get the car?"because we

00:15:17.279 --> 00:15:19.189
only had one car, "and drive her around

00:15:19.199 --> 00:15:21.430
just so she'll fall asleep while you're

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:23.750
driving around."Because we

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:25.269
couldn't even get her to fall asleep in

00:15:25.279 --> 00:15:27.430
the house because even

00:15:27.430 --> 00:15:27.440
clothes—she

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:30.150
didn't wear clothes for years

00:15:30.160 --> 00:15:32.310
because the touch of the clothing on her

00:15:32.320 --> 00:15:35.430
skin weirded her out and she'd have

00:15:35.440 --> 00:15:37.509
to take her clothes off.

00:15:37.519 --> 00:15:38.790
Everybody was thinking, "Well, this

00:15:38.800 --> 00:15:40.230
kid's just wearing a diaper."We got her

00:15:40.230 --> 00:15:40.240
to

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:42.470
where she'd wear a diaper in

00:15:42.480 --> 00:15:44.710
public because she

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:46.949
didn't even want to have a diaper on, and

00:15:46.959 --> 00:15:49.350
so she'd try to be nude because she

00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:50.790
didn't want the texture of the diaper

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:53.110
on. So we had to get her to the point

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:54.470
where she would just wear a diaper, and

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:57.110
we were ecstatic about that. Then we

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:59.430
were ecstatic just to get a t-shirt

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:01.910
on her,

00:16:01.910 --> 00:16:01.920
or

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:04.389
one of those big princess dresses.

00:16:04.399 --> 00:16:06.310
We tried to put one of those

00:16:06.310 --> 00:16:06.320
nightgowns

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:07.670
on her, so she would walk around with a

00:16:07.670 --> 00:16:07.680
nightgown

00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:10.389
on. It took us

00:16:10.399 --> 00:16:12.230
another year or so before we got her

00:16:12.240 --> 00:16:15.990
there. And it was like all this time was

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:18.550
pressure, pressure, pressure. And it

00:16:18.560 --> 00:16:20.389
molds you. And what happens with the

00:16:20.399 --> 00:16:22.230
diamond whenever that coal is under

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:25.470
pressure? It

00:16:25.470 --> 00:16:25.480
transforms

00:16:25.480 --> 00:16:28.389
into something so beautiful.

00:16:28.399 --> 00:16:30.710
But without the pressure, it would never

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:32.389
transform into what it was

00:16:32.399 --> 00:16:34.790
supposed to be. Just like it is with

00:16:34.790 --> 00:16:34.800
a

00:16:34.800 --> 00:16:37.990
caterpillar. You have a

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:40.790
beautiful caterpillar in a cocoon. And

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:43.430
if you remove that cocoon

00:16:43.440 --> 00:16:45.829
before it's time and they

00:16:45.839 --> 00:16:47.590
don't have the strength—the

00:16:47.590 --> 00:16:47.600
monarch

00:16:47.600 --> 00:16:49.590
butterfly has the strength

00:16:49.600 --> 00:16:53.110
to push against that

00:16:53.110 --> 00:16:53.120
cocoon—it

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:55.269
will never develop

00:16:55.279 --> 00:16:57.470
the strength to

00:16:57.480 --> 00:17:01.990
fly. The pressure of the cocoon

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:05.189
makes that

00:17:05.199 --> 00:17:07.029
caterpillar that turns

00:17:07.039 --> 00:17:09.829
into a butterfly into who

00:17:09.839 --> 00:17:13.110
it is. And without that pressure on its

00:17:13.120 --> 00:17:15.189
life, it will never be what it's

00:17:15.199 --> 00:17:17.669
supposed to be because we think, "Well,

00:17:17.679 --> 00:17:19.590
we'll just remove that off of

00:17:19.590 --> 00:17:19.600
there."But

00:17:19.600 --> 00:17:21.750
if you remove that pressure of

00:17:21.760 --> 00:17:23.949
him trying to fight to get out of

00:17:23.959 --> 00:17:26.309
that, that caterpillar wouldn't be a

00:17:26.319 --> 00:17:28.950
beautiful monarch butterfly.

00:17:28.960 --> 00:17:31.430
So, a lot of times I see what

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:33.110
people go through. They think that

00:17:33.120 --> 00:17:35.190
the storms of life are destroying

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:36.710
them, but yet they're

00:17:36.720 --> 00:17:39.430
making them into who they are. The

00:17:39.440 --> 00:17:41.430
pressure of life develops you into

00:17:41.440 --> 00:17:42.590
something

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:45.990
great. We think, 'God, can you remove this

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:49.110
or

00:17:49.110 --> 00:17:49.120
that?'But

00:17:49.120 --> 00:17:52.549
He tells you today, 'All

00:17:52.559 --> 00:17:54.710
things are possible to him that

00:17:54.710 --> 00:17:54.720
believes.'And

00:17:54.720 --> 00:17:56.710
not only that, 'Son, I'm going to turn

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:59.669
it around for good. What the devil meant

00:17:59.679 --> 00:18:01.190
for bad, I'm going to turn for good in

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:03.590
your favor.'That's what He's trying to

00:18:03.600 --> 00:18:05.230
tell you

00:18:05.240 --> 00:18:08.390
all. Don't always embrace it; fight and

00:18:08.400 --> 00:18:10.470
resist it. Just like that caterpillar is

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:12.310
up there fighting and that butterfly is

00:18:12.320 --> 00:18:14.270
going, 'I want out of this! I want out of

00:18:14.270 --> 00:18:14.280
this!'Fight

00:18:14.280 --> 00:18:17.750
spiritually against it.

00:18:17.760 --> 00:18:21.029
Don't embrace it and coddle it.

00:18:21.039 --> 00:18:24.630
Resist it. Submit yourself therefore

00:18:24.640 --> 00:18:27.789
unto God. Resist the devil and he will

00:18:27.799 --> 00:18:31.590
flee. But when trials and

00:18:31.600 --> 00:18:33.750
things happen, we fight against them

00:18:33.750 --> 00:18:33.760
and

00:18:33.760 --> 00:18:35.950
we won't let

00:18:35.950 --> 00:18:35.960
them

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:38.630
stay. But the process of the

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:41.350
fight is what changes us. A

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:43.750
lot of times it's the word; it's staying

00:18:43.760 --> 00:18:47.350
the course. And in this situation,

00:18:47.360 --> 00:18:51.110
like I said, God did not do this.

00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:52.870
The devil comes to kill, steal, and

00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:54.870
destroy. But the Bible says that He

00:18:54.870 --> 00:18:54.880
has

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:56.390
come that we might have life, and life

00:18:56.400 --> 00:18:59.510
more abundantly. But in this situation,

00:18:59.520 --> 00:19:02.310
it's what I needed obviously to develop

00:19:02.320 --> 00:19:05.510
who I was a little bit more. And

00:19:05.520 --> 00:19:08.150
whenever it was all over, He preached me

00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:11.029
a sermon. He encouraged me and told me

00:19:11.039 --> 00:19:12.630
there was a call on my life. He told me

00:19:12.640 --> 00:19:13.990
that He was going to use me for

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:16.470
ministry. He told me that this

00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:18.630
pressure that I was going

00:19:18.640 --> 00:19:21.190
through at the time would subside,

00:19:21.200 --> 00:19:23.110
that the storms of life would not always

00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:25.110
be there with the intensity of what it

00:19:25.120 --> 00:19:26.789
was then, but that we would

00:19:26.799 --> 00:19:29.110
always go from glory to glory to glory

00:19:29.120 --> 00:19:31.590
and we mature and we are able to handle

00:19:31.600 --> 00:19:33.510
that pressure a little better.

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:35.110
There's more pressure now than I've

00:19:35.120 --> 00:19:37.909
ever had before. But it's different.

00:19:37.919 --> 00:19:40.150
It's different because we're going from

00:19:40.160 --> 00:19:41.990
glory to glory, and that potter is

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:43.990
putting His hand on that clay and He's

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:46.150
molding us. We have this treasure in

00:19:46.150 --> 00:19:46.160
earthen

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:48.310
vessels that the excellency of

00:19:48.320 --> 00:19:49.830
the power will be known of Him and not

00:19:49.840 --> 00:19:52.150
of us. And if you think, 'Well, I've

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:55.190
derailed my life. I was a bad person. I

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:57.190
murdered, I raped, I robbed. I did

00:19:57.200 --> 00:19:59.909
whatever, and God can't use me

00:19:59.909 --> 00:19:59.919
now,'or

00:19:59.919 --> 00:20:02.870
'I was the victim of

00:20:02.870 --> 00:20:02.880
that,'—that's

00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:04.789
what I'm trying to say. You say, 'I was

00:20:04.799 --> 00:20:06.870
the victim of a rape. I was a victim of

00:20:06.870 --> 00:20:06.880
an

00:20:06.880 --> 00:20:09.990
abusive husband. I was a victim

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:12.710
of a sexually abusive father, or all

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:14.470
these things, and I'm disqualified.

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:17.669
God can't use me. I'm broken.'What the

00:20:17.679 --> 00:20:19.990
devil meant for bad to destroy you, God

00:20:19.990 --> 00:20:20.000
will

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:22.789
turn it around in your favor. What

00:20:22.789 --> 00:20:22.799
was

00:20:22.799 --> 00:20:24.710
meant to try to derail and

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:26.950
destroy you, He will

00:20:26.960 --> 00:20:31.990
take and turn into beauty from ashes.

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:34.070
And I'm telling you, don't give up on

00:20:34.080 --> 00:20:36.950
what you are believing for because those

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:39.430
circumstances and that pain are what's

00:20:39.440 --> 00:20:40.870
going to help you to help somebody else

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:42.950
that's walked through the pain and

00:20:42.950 --> 00:20:42.960
is

00:20:42.960 --> 00:20:44.789
walking through it right now. You'll be

00:20:44.799 --> 00:20:46.470
able to minister to somebody and have

00:20:46.480 --> 00:20:48.470
compassion on them when somebody else

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:49.909
won't. Like somebody who's been

00:20:49.919 --> 00:20:52.070
diagnosed with something really bad and

00:20:52.080 --> 00:20:53.270
you were diagnosed with it and God

00:20:53.280 --> 00:20:55.830
healed you. You have more compassion for

00:20:55.840 --> 00:20:58.549
that person, like I have for

00:20:58.559 --> 00:21:00.149
children with special needs. When

00:21:00.159 --> 00:21:01.750
I see a child with special needs in

00:21:01.760 --> 00:21:04.710
the store or whatever, my

00:21:04.710 --> 00:21:04.720
spirit

00:21:04.720 --> 00:21:08.070
literally weeps for them with

00:21:08.080 --> 00:21:10.470
the compassion that I have towards

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:13.430
families that are going through this and

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:15.190
I pray for them. I'm telling you, I

00:21:15.200 --> 00:21:17.270
have more compassion to pray for them

00:21:17.280 --> 00:21:19.270
than I have probably for anybody else

00:21:19.280 --> 00:21:21.830
because I've been through the pain. And

00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:23.430
when you walk through the pain of

00:21:23.440 --> 00:21:25.590
something, you're able to help

00:21:25.600 --> 00:21:27.590
somebody else that's going through it

00:21:27.600 --> 00:21:29.190
because you've been there. You've cried

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:31.430
those tears. You've held your

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:33.190
head up through the storm and you can

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:35.510
say to them, 'Hey, you can make it,

00:21:35.510 --> 00:21:35.520
too.'And

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:37.669
you may be going through the

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:38.950
storm and thinking, 'Man, I don't know

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:41.350
how I'm going to get through this. I

00:21:41.360 --> 00:21:42.390
don't know how I'm going to breathe

00:21:42.400 --> 00:21:43.909
another minute.'There were days I wanted

00:21:43.919 --> 00:21:46.710
to drive my car off the side of a bridge.

00:21:46.720 --> 00:21:49.190
I didn't care if I

00:21:49.200 --> 00:21:51.669
got hit by a train. That's how much pain

00:21:51.679 --> 00:21:53.669
I was going through on the way to work

00:21:53.679 --> 00:21:55.430
or on the way home because I knew

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.510
what I was facing when I got there. But

00:21:57.520 --> 00:21:59.830
I fought through it because I knew that

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:02.149
God had a plan for my life. But I'm

00:22:02.159 --> 00:22:04.789
talking about the darkest, darkest

00:22:04.799 --> 00:22:06.789
bottom of the pit, and you're thinking,

00:22:06.799 --> 00:22:08.510
'I don't think I'm going to make this.'There

00:22:08.510 --> 00:22:08.520
were

00:22:08.520 --> 00:22:10.789
days that were

00:22:10.799 --> 00:22:13.029
that dark. I'm just being real with

00:22:13.039 --> 00:22:15.029
y'all. You may not want to hear

00:22:15.039 --> 00:22:17.350
that, but it's real. This is raw. It's

00:22:17.360 --> 00:22:19.750
real, and you need to hear it.

00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:21.909
There were days that I thought, while cleaning,

00:22:21.919 --> 00:22:23.830
and you didn't have enough money to

00:22:23.840 --> 00:22:25.830
buy a gallon of milk, and you're

00:22:25.840 --> 00:22:27.029
thinking, 'God, I don't know how I'm

00:22:27.039 --> 00:22:31.110
going to make

00:22:31.110 --> 00:22:31.120
it.'Those

00:22:31.120 --> 00:22:32.789
days when you're crying yourself to

00:22:32.799 --> 00:22:35.750
sleep and nobody around you cares.

00:22:35.760 --> 00:22:37.430
Nobody around you is praying for you.

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:39.390
You felt like you're all

00:22:39.400 --> 00:22:41.669
alone. That's how I felt a lot of

00:22:41.679 --> 00:22:44.310
times. I'd go to work, being there in

00:22:44.310 --> 00:22:44.320
the

00:22:44.320 --> 00:22:46.630
bathrooms by myself cleaning, hearing my

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:48.549
wife cry, calling on the phone, crying,

00:22:48.559 --> 00:22:50.230
'I need your help. Pray for me. I'm

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:52.310
having a hard day with Megan. I need

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:54.149
this, I need that.'I was having

00:22:54.159 --> 00:22:56.630
a hard time myself, trying to pick

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:58.950
myself up from

00:22:58.950 --> 00:22:58.960
this, and

00:22:58.960 --> 00:23:01.590
you think inside, 'But God. But

00:23:01.600 --> 00:23:05.950
God.'My

00:23:05.960 --> 00:23:08.630
hope is built on nothing less

00:23:08.640 --> 00:23:10.549
than Jesus's blood and His

00:23:10.559 --> 00:23:13.110
righteousness. I believe with all my

00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:16.070
heart that by the stripes of Jesus,

00:23:16.080 --> 00:23:18.070
Megan is healed.

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:19.990
And in the process of believing for the

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:20.990
full

00:23:20.990 --> 00:23:21.000
manifestation—sometimes

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:24.149
it's a process,

00:23:24.159 --> 00:23:26.470
but a miracle is a miracle. Even if it's

00:23:26.470 --> 00:23:26.480
day-to-day,

00:23:26.480 --> 00:23:31.190
if you're

00:23:31.200 --> 00:23:33.710
seeing change, it's still a

00:23:33.720 --> 00:23:37.590
miracle. Jesus... sometimes it's a

00:23:37.600 --> 00:23:39.789
progressive thing. I've seen

00:23:39.799 --> 00:23:43.430
it in my own life and I still believe,

00:23:43.440 --> 00:23:45.270
and I'm still standing. And people say,

00:23:45.280 --> 00:23:46.470
'Well, shouldn't you have your full

00:23:46.480 --> 00:23:49.990
manifestation yet?'I've given up on

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:51.750
trying to sit there and figure things

00:23:51.760 --> 00:23:54.190
out. I trust

00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:56.430
Him. In Him, I trust

00:23:56.440 --> 00:23:59.590
with all my

00:23:59.600 --> 00:24:01.590
heart, all my mind, all my soul, and all

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:03.669
my strength. I lean not

00:24:03.679 --> 00:24:05.750
unto my own understanding,

00:24:05.760 --> 00:24:07.270
but in all thy

00:24:07.280 --> 00:24:08.710
ways acknowledge Him, and He said, 'He

00:24:08.710 --> 00:24:08.720
shall

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:10.950
direct your paths.'I lean not unto my

00:24:10.960 --> 00:24:11.710
own

00:24:11.720 --> 00:24:13.830
understanding because I have a thousand

00:24:13.830 --> 00:24:13.840
and

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:15.909
one things... why... you could get upset

00:24:15.919 --> 00:24:17.190
about it and say, 'Well, Lord, do you

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:19.510
hear my prayers? Lord, where are you

00:24:19.520 --> 00:24:21.909
at? Why has the full manifestation of

00:24:21.919 --> 00:24:24.070
this not happened yet? Why is she

00:24:24.080 --> 00:24:26.710
still not talking? Why is she still

00:24:26.720 --> 00:24:28.310
doing this? Why is she still doing

00:24:28.310 --> 00:24:28.320
that?'But

00:24:28.320 --> 00:24:31.070
I say, 'I trust

00:24:31.080 --> 00:24:33.830
you, Father. Not my will, but yours be

00:24:33.830 --> 00:24:33.840
done.'When

00:24:33.840 --> 00:24:36.470
the manifestation

00:24:36.470 --> 00:24:36.480
comes—with

00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:38.070
the full manifestation,

00:24:38.070 --> 00:24:38.080
God—we

00:24:38.080 --> 00:24:39.909
give you all the glory, all

00:24:39.919 --> 00:24:43.350
honor, and all the praise regardless.

00:24:43.360 --> 00:24:45.870
I choose to worship

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:49.350
you. I choose to worship you. And that's

00:24:49.360 --> 00:24:52.470
where we remain concerning these things.

00:24:52.470 --> 00:24:52.480
I

00:24:52.480 --> 00:24:53.789
used

00:24:53.789 --> 00:24:53.799
to

00:24:53.799 --> 00:24:56.310
always complain, 'Like I said, I

00:24:56.320 --> 00:24:57.590
can't go out and lay hands on these

00:24:57.600 --> 00:24:58.789
people. I can't do all this

00:24:58.789 --> 00:24:58.799
stuff.'And

00:24:58.799 --> 00:25:00.990
the Lord said,

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:04.070
'Brandon, Megan does not validate my word

00:25:04.080 --> 00:25:06.789
in the manifestation of her healing. My

00:25:06.799 --> 00:25:09.669
word validates itself. It's a pillar and

00:25:09.679 --> 00:25:12.549
it stands alone. I don't need Megan's

00:25:12.559 --> 00:25:14.470
full manifestation for you to

00:25:14.480 --> 00:25:16.230
go out and

00:25:16.240 --> 00:25:18.390
tell people that I'm a healer and lay

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:21.269
hands on people and see them recover. My

00:25:21.279 --> 00:25:25.669
word is enough. My word is enough. I

00:25:25.679 --> 00:25:27.510
don't need you to have a full

00:25:27.520 --> 00:25:29.990
manifestation of something for you to do

00:25:30.000 --> 00:25:32.190
in obedience what I've called you to

00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:35.510
do. Do what I called you to do and

00:25:35.520 --> 00:25:36.830
don't worry about the

00:25:36.830 --> 00:25:36.840
rest.'My

00:25:36.840 --> 00:25:40.470
word is a pillar.

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:43.110
When He said, 'By my stripes you are

00:25:43.110 --> 00:25:43.120
healed,'in

00:25:43.120 --> 00:25:45.510
Galatians, Christ redeemed

00:25:45.520 --> 00:25:47.510
me from the curse of the law and He told

00:25:47.520 --> 00:25:50.310
me, He said, 'That's the foundation

00:25:50.310 --> 00:25:50.320
regardless.'I'm

00:25:50.320 --> 00:25:53.110
not moved by what I see.

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:55.669
I'm not moved by what I feel. I'm moved

00:25:55.679 --> 00:25:58.870
by what the word of God says. So back to

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:01.350
what I was saying right

00:26:01.360 --> 00:26:03.269
before, when I'm taken out of my body and

00:26:03.279 --> 00:26:05.990
I'm standing at the hospital

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.750
in this portal, I went through all this

00:26:07.760 --> 00:26:09.350
stuff and He's doing all this, I could

00:26:09.360 --> 00:26:11.830
feel the sun. I could feel the

00:26:11.830 --> 00:26:11.840
pressure.

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:14.230
I could see the strain, all of

00:26:14.240 --> 00:26:16.310
it. And he said, this is what he said to

00:26:16.320 --> 00:26:18.190
me: 'Go

00:26:18.200 --> 00:26:22.070
back and give your daughter a hug and

00:26:22.080 --> 00:26:25.110
love on her and thank her right now for

00:26:25.120 --> 00:26:26.789
everything that's going on

00:26:26.799 --> 00:26:29.590
with your life. Thank her. Don't

00:26:29.600 --> 00:26:34.230
curse it anymore. Just

00:26:34.240 --> 00:26:36.870
stay in an atmosphere of praise, not

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:39.510
towards her, but towards me. Change the

00:26:39.510 --> 00:26:39.520
complaining,'because

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:40.870
I was complaining

00:26:40.880 --> 00:26:43.269
all the time. I was complaining about, 'I

00:26:43.279 --> 00:26:44.390
don't like being, I don't want to raise

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:45.830
this, I don't want to do

00:26:45.830 --> 00:26:45.840
that.'I

00:26:45.840 --> 00:26:46.830
was always

00:26:46.830 --> 00:26:46.840
mean;

00:26:46.840 --> 00:26:49.990
my mouth was terrible, speaking

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:51.350
things out of my mouth. 'I don't want to

00:26:51.360 --> 00:26:52.710
do this anymore. I don't want to live

00:26:52.720 --> 00:26:53.630
this

00:26:53.630 --> 00:26:53.640
anymore.'And

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:55.750
I got to the point where I said,

00:26:55.760 --> 00:26:58.310
'Thank you, Father. Thank you. Thank

00:26:58.310 --> 00:26:58.320
you.'And

00:26:58.320 --> 00:26:59.590
then I got home and I held

00:26:59.600 --> 00:27:02.149
Megan. I said, 'Megan, I love you. I

00:27:02.159 --> 00:27:03.830
just want to tell you I love you and

00:27:03.830 --> 00:27:03.840
Daddy's

00:27:03.840 --> 00:27:05.990
sorry that I didn't hear Him

00:27:06.000 --> 00:27:08.230
right, but thank you. Your life is

00:27:08.240 --> 00:27:09.149
changing

00:27:09.159 --> 00:27:12.549
me. The Lord through you, Megan,

00:27:12.559 --> 00:27:14.669
is changing your daddy.'That was

00:27:14.679 --> 00:27:19.549
hard. The Lord through

00:27:19.559 --> 00:27:23.510
you is changing a

00:27:23.520 --> 00:27:24.830
man that needed

00:27:24.840 --> 00:27:27.669
help. And I'm sorry I had to be

00:27:27.679 --> 00:27:30.870
like this, but I thank you for

00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:33.909
your life and I pray for you and it's

00:27:33.919 --> 00:27:36.630
going to get better. But all things work

00:27:36.640 --> 00:27:38.230
together for good for those that love

00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:40.630
the Lord. And some people may not want

00:27:40.640 --> 00:27:43.269
to hear that. But sometimes people need

00:27:43.279 --> 00:27:45.750
to hear reality: whenever you're going

00:27:45.760 --> 00:27:47.750
through something and the

00:27:47.760 --> 00:27:49.470
storms of life are trying to knock you

00:27:49.480 --> 00:27:52.630
down, you've got to keep on keeping on

00:27:52.640 --> 00:27:54.389
and believe that all things are

00:27:54.399 --> 00:27:56.710
possible to him that believes and that

00:27:56.720 --> 00:27:58.389
Jesus is the healer still

00:27:58.389 --> 00:27:58.399
today—yesterday,

00:27:58.399 --> 00:28:00.549
today, and forever. And the

00:28:00.559 --> 00:28:02.149
same God that healed the sick back then

00:28:02.159 --> 00:28:04.389
is healing the sick today. And you

00:28:04.399 --> 00:28:06.149
cannot give up on what you're believing

00:28:06.159 --> 00:28:07.909
for. Do not give up on your unsaved

00:28:07.919 --> 00:28:10.230
loved ones. Do not give up on your

00:28:10.240 --> 00:28:12.710
unhealed ones that don't have

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:14.310
the full manifestation of what they're

00:28:14.320 --> 00:28:16.310
believing for. And some people say,

00:28:16.320 --> 00:28:18.389
'Well, they died and they never got

00:28:18.389 --> 00:28:18.399
it.'Well,

00:28:18.399 --> 00:28:20.630
why didn't they get it

00:28:20.640 --> 00:28:22.350
on this side? I can't answer those

00:28:22.360 --> 00:28:24.710
questions. I've seen people that

00:28:24.720 --> 00:28:26.710
I've been praying for and they

00:28:26.720 --> 00:28:28.630
don't get the full manifestation on this

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:30.470
side. People are devastated by it

00:28:30.480 --> 00:28:31.750
and they say, 'Well, God didn't

00:28:31.760 --> 00:28:33.029
love us. God didn't do

00:28:33.029 --> 00:28:33.039
that.'No,

00:28:33.039 --> 00:28:36.389
always stay on

00:28:36.399 --> 00:28:38.710
God's side. No matter if you don't

00:28:38.720 --> 00:28:40.149
understand why you're going through what

00:28:40.159 --> 00:28:42.510
you're going through, stay on God's

00:28:42.520 --> 00:28:46.230
side. Always see God as a good God.

00:28:46.240 --> 00:28:49.590
Always. No matter how hard the trial, no

00:28:49.600 --> 00:28:53.029
matter how much the pain, always stay on

00:28:53.039 --> 00:28:54.110
God's

00:28:54.120 --> 00:28:58.630
side. Always praise God. Always worship

00:28:58.640 --> 00:29:02.149
God through the storms of life. And in

00:29:02.159 --> 00:29:05.750
that it becomes beautiful. It

00:29:05.760 --> 00:29:08.630
will change you, not because

00:29:08.640 --> 00:29:10.510
it's not the truth, but because of the

00:29:10.510 --> 00:29:10.520
truth—God's

00:29:10.520 --> 00:29:14.549
truth. God is love.

00:29:14.559 --> 00:29:17.750
God loves you. And yeah, things happen

00:29:17.760 --> 00:29:20.230
and things that are hard happen. And

00:29:20.240 --> 00:29:22.070
if I would have heard the voice of the

00:29:22.080 --> 00:29:25.149
Lord not to get that and do

00:29:25.159 --> 00:29:28.149
that, I'd have been a real rascal still

00:29:28.159 --> 00:29:30.310
for what I saw.

00:29:30.320 --> 00:29:32.389
But it was the pressure that changed me.

00:29:32.399 --> 00:29:34.149
Could he have used another kind of pressure?

00:29:34.159 --> 00:29:36.549
I'm sure he could have. But it

00:29:36.559 --> 00:29:38.389
was an illustration of what he showed me

00:29:38.399 --> 00:29:41.669
about me. And if anybody knew who I was

00:29:41.679 --> 00:29:43.269
back then, I'm not that same person

00:29:43.279 --> 00:29:45.909
anymore. That person died a long time ago.

00:29:45.919 --> 00:29:48.950
He's

00:29:48.960 --> 00:29:51.909
not alive like that

00:29:51.909 --> 00:29:51.919
anymore.

00:29:51.919 --> 00:29:55.590
I had a lot of issues and the Lord has

00:29:55.600 --> 00:29:58.310
molded me and He has made me into who

00:29:58.320 --> 00:30:00.230
I am today, able to stand before

00:30:00.240 --> 00:30:01.950
you all and do what I'm doing today.

00:30:01.960 --> 00:30:04.549
I just wanted to minister to

00:30:04.559 --> 00:30:06.149
you a little bit and to tell you, don't

00:30:06.159 --> 00:30:08.230
give up on your circumstance;

00:30:08.240 --> 00:30:09.870
you're not big enough to mess your life

00:30:09.880 --> 00:30:13.269
up. You're not big enough. No matter how

00:30:13.279 --> 00:30:15.190
much you think, 'Well, I was in prison

00:30:15.200 --> 00:30:16.950
for 20 years,'or 'I was doing this,

00:30:16.960 --> 00:30:19.430
I've done

00:30:19.430 --> 00:30:19.440
that,'you're

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:24.510
not big enough to mess your life

00:30:24.520 --> 00:30:27.029
up. The steps of the righteous are

00:30:27.039 --> 00:30:28.269
ordered of the

00:30:28.279 --> 00:30:31.029
Lord.

00:30:31.039 --> 00:30:33.190
And whatever the

00:30:33.200 --> 00:30:36.149
devil meant for bad, the Lord will turn

00:30:36.159 --> 00:30:38.750
it around for good in your

00:30:38.760 --> 00:30:41.909
favor. Remember that today. And you've

00:30:41.919 --> 00:30:43.710
got to trust that He

00:30:43.720 --> 00:30:46.630
will. Trust in the

00:30:46.640 --> 00:30:47.990
Lord with all your heart and lean not

00:30:48.000 --> 00:30:50.149
unto your own understanding, but in all thy

00:30:50.159 --> 00:30:52.389
ways acknowledge Him and He said He

00:30:52.399 --> 00:30:56.909
would direct your path. So let me

00:30:56.909 --> 00:30:56.919
encourage—what

00:30:56.919 --> 00:30:58.950
I said is fine, put

00:30:58.960 --> 00:31:01.029
it on a shelf. But this is my life and

00:31:01.039 --> 00:31:03.510
I'm telling you what I've walked.

00:31:03.520 --> 00:31:04.430
Everyone's

00:31:04.440 --> 00:31:07.990
into

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:09.990
whatever the

00:31:10.000 --> 00:31:12.230
Lord's had for them, but I'm trying to

00:31:12.240 --> 00:31:14.230
tell you all what I've learned and

00:31:14.240 --> 00:31:16.710
how I'm growing and how we're all

00:31:16.710 --> 00:31:16.720
a

00:31:16.720 --> 00:31:19.230
work in

00:31:19.240 --> 00:31:21.430
progress. So, Father, I thank you

00:31:21.440 --> 00:31:23.909
for every single person that is

00:31:23.919 --> 00:31:25.549
represented here

00:31:25.559 --> 00:31:27.830
today. I thank you, Father, for your

00:31:27.840 --> 00:31:31.310
visitations and manifestations of your

00:31:31.320 --> 00:31:33.669
glory. I thank you, Father, that no

00:31:33.679 --> 00:31:37.909
weapon formed against us shall prosper.

00:31:37.919 --> 00:31:40.149
I thank you, Father, that

00:31:40.159 --> 00:31:42.470
you said in your word that

00:31:42.480 --> 00:31:44.029
you have a plan for

00:31:44.039 --> 00:31:47.750
us and you have a path for us and

00:31:47.760 --> 00:31:50.710
that we will find it. Father, by

00:31:50.720 --> 00:31:54.470
seeking you daily, we will find it. And

00:31:54.480 --> 00:31:58.149
you said, 'Beloved, I wish

00:31:58.159 --> 00:31:59.750
above all things that you prosper and be

00:31:59.760 --> 00:32:02.110
in health, even as your soul

00:32:02.120 --> 00:32:05.750
prospers.'How

00:32:05.760 --> 00:32:08.549
much more, Father, that you are the

00:32:08.559 --> 00:32:10.230
great creator,

00:32:10.240 --> 00:32:12.070
the great Father that you are? You

00:32:12.080 --> 00:32:14.230
have that beautiful plan planned out for

00:32:14.240 --> 00:32:16.230
every single one of us. And it's not to

00:32:16.240 --> 00:32:18.950
harm us; it's not to hurt us. And if the

00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:21.590
devil tries to throw a big log in

00:32:21.600 --> 00:32:23.909
our path and we stumble on it,

00:32:23.919 --> 00:32:25.750
Father, that you'll turn that into

00:32:25.760 --> 00:32:27.950
toothpicks that we can pick our teeth

00:32:27.960 --> 00:32:30.789
with. I just know

00:32:30.799 --> 00:32:33.430
that you're so faithful.

00:32:33.440 --> 00:32:35.669
I know, Father, that

00:32:35.679 --> 00:32:37.350
you have a plan for each and

00:32:37.360 --> 00:32:41.350
every single person here. And God,

00:32:41.360 --> 00:32:44.310
as long as we have air and breath in

00:32:44.320 --> 00:32:47.470
our lungs and we have praise on our

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:49.990
lips, I thank you, Father, that we

00:32:50.000 --> 00:32:52.350
praise you even in the

00:32:52.360 --> 00:32:54.789
storms. We

00:32:54.799 --> 00:32:56.950
praise you in the good times.

00:32:56.960 --> 00:32:59.269
We praise you in the hard times. We

00:32:59.279 --> 00:33:00.950
praise you in the times that we feel

00:33:00.960 --> 00:33:02.310
like we're not going to make it,

00:33:04.960 --> 00:33:07.909
and we learn to

00:33:07.919 --> 00:33:09.990
praise you in all areas of our life, not

00:33:10.000 --> 00:33:13.590
just in the good. But God, we praise

00:33:13.600 --> 00:33:15.669
you even greater in the dark times. And

00:33:15.679 --> 00:33:19.269
we say, 'God is faithful and God is able

00:33:19.279 --> 00:33:22.710
to deliver us from this darkness. God

00:33:22.720 --> 00:33:26.230
has done it and we will receive it

00:33:26.230 --> 00:33:26.240
now.'Now

00:33:26.240 --> 00:33:28.430
God, I speak healing over their

00:33:28.430 --> 00:33:28.440
bodies—every

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:30.630
single person who's

00:33:30.640 --> 00:33:32.870
believing for a creative miracle,

00:33:32.880 --> 00:33:34.870
from the top of their head

00:33:34.870 --> 00:33:34.880
to

00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:37.590
something that seemed to

00:33:37.600 --> 00:33:41.190
linger on forever. There's

00:33:41.200 --> 00:33:44.389
always a suddenly; there's always

00:33:44.399 --> 00:33:46.549
a time whenever the manifestation of

00:33:46.559 --> 00:33:48.830
what you're believing for

00:33:48.840 --> 00:33:52.389
manifests. And I believe that today is

00:33:52.399 --> 00:33:55.029
their day for their deliverance.

00:33:55.039 --> 00:33:57.430
It's like he told me

00:33:57.440 --> 00:33:58.950
